      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DELULU (9) has the hoof on the till after placing in all three starts so far this campaign. Was very brave from this barrier last week, racing three wide without cover but digging deep to miss by a nose. Should be peaking now and with a touch better luck she could break through. HILLVIEW BONDI (8) will enjoy a class drop having tackled stronger company in his two starts so far this time in. Draws wide again but is building in fitness. This is winnable with even luck. SKYLORD (10) has yet to fire this time in but he too should find this easier. Draws on the back row but owns a good third-up record so could be ready to produce his best. IMA FIVESTAR GENERAL NZ (5) usually performs well when resuming so keep him safe.",
